messages.message:
My apologies for the late reply on this. This are very minor performance improvements. However, limitations include:

1. The user would need to wait for the flow to complete before moving on to doing anything else. This stands in contrast to running apps "normally", where they can start a flow and check back anytime.
2. The results of the job are not stored anywhere
3. Our CDN timeout configs on prod is currently causing requests to fail; we are currently working on this
